Description:
There are some mandarin speaker positions that we currently open: GA staff, Finance Staff, Purchasing Staff, HR Staff, and Administration Staff, qualification:
Minimum education: S1 in any major. Relevant Mandarin Translation, Linguistics certifications or a related field or equivalent experience will also be considered;
Work confidence, good at grasping the details of the work, good at finding and analyzing problems;
Have a strong sense of pioneering and innovative, flexible adaptability;
Cheerful personality, good teamwork spirit and communication;
Proficiency in operating Microsoft office;
Fresh Graduates are welcome to apply.
